(firstQuint)A Study of BiZact on Children and Adolescents Undergoing Tonsillectomy.

 A prospective, multi-center, single arm, study of BiZact cent on children and adolescents undergoing tonsillectomy.

 Study Visits: - Screening/Baseline - Surgery, Day 0 - Post-Op Follow-up Day 1 - Day 7, Day 10, & Day 14 (Home assessments) - Post-Op Follow-up Day 28 (Office Visit).

 A Study of BiZact on Children and Adolescents Undergoing Tonsillectomy@highlight

The purpose of this study is to assess safety and performance with the use of the BiZact cent device in tonsillectomy procedures in children and adolescents.

